Statistics we might want to collect to snoop on people and get an idea of
where the load is and what people are doing lots of or little of etc:

Regions:
  occupancy vs. time (occupancy in terms of avatars OR objects in general)
  maximum occupancy
  fraction of population visited
  transaction rate vs. time
  maximum transaction rate
  fraction of time active

Avatars:
  hours logged in
  transaction rate vs. time
  maximum transaction rate
  minimum time between transactions
  maximum time between transactions
  transaction type vs. transaction number
  regions visited
  number of different regions visited
  number of region transitions
  region transition rate

Classes:
  number of instances

Objects:
  time active vs. time dormant
  number of transactions
